gedit 0.9.7 (September 10, 2001)

  Requirements updated

    * gedit has been updated to require the latest stable versions
      of software from the GNOME 1.4 release.  This means you will
      need the following for gedit:

	** libglade 0.16
	** gnome-libs 1.2.13
	** gnome-print 0.28
	** gnome-vfs 1.0
	** gtk+ 1.2.9 

    * Improved plugin manager (Paolo)
    * When in notebook mode, the active document can be changed
      with Ctrl+Page_up & Ctrl+Page_down (Phlip <pplumlee@omnigon.com>, Chema)
		
  Updates

    * Translations: Norwegian, Swedish, Finnish, German, Spanish,
      Slovakian, Russian, Chinese, Japanese.

  Bug Fixes

    * Small bug fixes and code cleanups. (Jason, Paolo, Chema)
    * Fix the recent menu entries that contain accelerators (Chema)

Enjoy.

