gedit 0.9.4 (Nov 24, 2000)

gedit 0.9.4, codename "Bruta ciega sordomuda torpe traste testaruda"
has been released.

gedit is a light-weight text editor for your cool Gnome desktop.

	 New in this release :
		- Fixed the recent file brokenes (Paolo) 
		- Reorganization of the toolbar & the find dialog (Paolo)
		- Gedit now handles MDI mode changes gracefully (Paolo)
		- Other bug fixes (Chema, Paolo)
		
	 Updated Translations :
		- Finnish - Jarkko Ranta <jjranta@cc.joensuu.fi>
		- & Others ..

Download at :
http://sourceforge.net/project/filelist.php?group_id=7
[Alternate : ftp://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/stable/sources/gedit]

Webpage :
http://gedit.sourceforge.net

Requirements :
gedit 0.9.4 requires gnome-print 0.25

Future :
	We are not adding new features before GNOME 1.4. After 1.4, we
plan to either port it to the new text gtk widget, bonobize gedit or both.

enjoy,
Chema


	   
